{"tid":2345757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰副主席換人　新任國航黨委書記宋志勇接任","createTime":"2020-12-29T19:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T03:16:03.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd178662cc179d6bd7ac446c1b064a44eed8bf08","tid":2345757,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T19:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201229-1320copy_5wZAi_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201229-1320copy_5wZAi_1200x0.png&h=af254964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空（0293）今日（29 日）宣布，持國泰 3 成股份的中國國際航空公司董事長蔡劍江，辭任國泰副主席和非常務董事，由新任國航董事長、黨委書記宋志勇接替。<br />\n<br />\n現年 55 歲的宋志勇，現任國航（0753）董事長、黨委書記，於中國空軍第一飛行學院畢業。宋志勇在 1987 年加入國航，2010 年 12 月任中航集團公司黨組成員，2014 年 3 月起任國泰非執董，2016 年 12 月擔任中航集團公司副董事長、總經理、黨組副書記。國泰表示，宋志勇每年可收取 57.5 萬元董事酬金。<br />\n<br />\n通告又指，蔡劍江今日已經辭任國航董事長及非執行董事。國泰表示，蔡劍江自 2009 年 11 月底獲委任為公司董事，董事局衷心感謝他過往的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%8F%9B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%96%B0%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E9%BB%A8%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E5%AE%8B%E5%BF%97%E5%8B%87%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%258F%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%25AE%258B%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%258E%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=bea3a65b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%258F%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6